{
  "texts": [
    "The XL-Sum dataset encompasses 1.35M pairs of professionally annotated articles and summaries, extracted from BBC through heuristic approaches, exclusively tailored for text summarization tasks.",
    "Encompassing 45 languages, over two-thirds of which qualify as low-resource languages, the dataset is designed to facilitate research in multilingual summarization.",
    "• XSum (Narayan et al, 2018).",
    "Functioning as a dataset tailored for singledocument summarization tasks, XSum draws its content from online articles curated by the British Broadcasting Corporation.",
    "Spanning the timeframe from 2010 to 2017, this dataset explores diverse domains, including family, science, and weather."
  ]
}